{"tid":1478303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「今次睇你點兜」 3M 1621 安全眼鏡測試","createTime":"2019-08-16T12:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T12:57:39.000Z","uid":176508,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c735dda2ead0d21f55908f15f899d5c276cafd29","tid":1478303,"uid":176508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1710262555863625/posts/2455411724682034?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1710262555863625%2Fposts%2F2455411724682034%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0RURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=cb4b9cc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1710262555863625/posts/2455411724682034?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【流言終結者\b－鋼珠破安全眼鏡？】<br />\n3M&trade; 1621 安全眼鏡，符合美國標準 ANSI Z87.1，可抵撞高速衝擊，鋼珠高速射都打唔穿，不過子彈就難講啲.....<br />\n<br />\n高速衝擊測試：<br />\n以 1/4 吋鋼珠以時速164公里撞擊。<br />\n高處撞擊測試：<br />\n1.1 磅物體由1.27米高處撞擊<br />\n<br />\n3M&trade; 1621 安全眼鏡<br />\n<a href=\"https://mall.builderhood.com/3m-1621.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmall.builderhood.com%2F3m-1621.html&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0RURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=711fc27c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mall.builderhood.com/3m-1621.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#無時間拍用住外國片先<br />\n#擋到鋼珠但子彈應該唔得<br />\n#咁鐘意做實驗咪買副返去驗<br />\n<br />\n影片來源：Testing Safety Eyewear : 3M Safety Eye Protection Impact Test"},{"pid":"0fbafbcbe561baa60b0ea9b84c2ad16c5efe788e","tid":1478303,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/uz68KJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuz68KJX.png&h=a0c87415&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08b4af84d959b5992a18783d5744b1000a42884c","tid":1478303,"uid":176508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d3fecb2